{"title":"Riñón de mieloma-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/Riñón de mieloma-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Riñón de\\Nmieloma","guid":"gTDpEfYR38P0wtIuobL_Ww","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"- Perlas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Cuál es la causa más común de\\Ninjuria renal aguda en MM?","guid":"4UCHTBriLIuOkOAYZ_FD_Q","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"- Nefropatía por\\Ncilindros (1).","guid":"FIvgHbZyinfWH3Tvrxn3PA","children":[]}]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Qué porcentaje de pacientes con\\NMM tienen falla renal al diagnóstico?","guid":"SBuABdX66blKre7EoICFKA","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"- 20-50% (1).","guid":"YtCwBOChGjFUlnNeqGEJ6Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Cuál es el mecanismo patogénico\\Nprincipal de daño renal en MM?","guid":"-vbdGQIg6OYW7XC3nZN4dg","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"- Exceso de cadenas\\Nligeras monoclonales (1).","guid":"RbtrD2S08ztB-vuWw_b4wg","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Qué toxicidad renal se asocia\\Nespecialmente a IgD y CL en MM?","guid":"heOjUfkA83PST5DetECqVw","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"- Insuficiencia\\Nrenal aguda (1).","guid":"UUzF5PJpVT-RMw01kCY9Jg","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"- ¿Cuál es la supervivencia mediana en ERCT\\Npor MM con quimioterapia convencional?","guid":"q-fHEfy4mOhHvWy9XCykhg","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"- 4-8 meses (1).","guid":"UYxGa8rUBEI_cOA4NHkLiA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"0","text":"Gamapatias monoclonales\\NParaproteína","guid":"M_sG-z0rjJBshec2ohZqEw","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"Linfocito B","guid":"iJekDOJDheeOydtg07uanQ","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• Macroglobulinemia de Waldenstrom","guid":"tdvQU16TfxI_3YZVIuXW9A","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"• GMSI IgM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"13","text":"• Linfoma Linfoplasmocítico","guid":"WSYmMjqrb36TJKd75orXAg","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"13","text":"• LLC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"13","text":"• Linfoma marginal esplénico","guid":"zRLXNXkS-UzJpY8P7DYSeQ","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"13","text":"• MALT","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"13","text":"• Linfoma Folicular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"13","text":"• DCGB...","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"12","text":"Plasmocito","guid":"wx-XjhqXx2wiOtidqBjohQ","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"• Gamapatía monoclonal de significado incierto no IgM (GMSI no IgM)","guid":"fC_EBsIGtGvfPT-VsQURLA","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"• Gamapatía monoclonal de significado renal (GMSR)","guid":"UUNxCZAJeqGGmdG0J7cFQQ","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"• Mieloma múltiple smoldering (SMM)","guid":"dqkSymnqTD1-BgZD2G9pJA","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"22","text":"• MM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"22","text":"• POEMS","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"22","text":"• Plasmocitoma (óseo y extraóseo/solita o múltiple)","guid":"VMXvA1VaFD7v7OF9w5HNLA","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"22","text":"• Leucemia de células plasmáticas","guid":"YXh8kdUBx88bVGEAHA6OQA","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"22","text":"• Amiloidosis primaria (AL)...","guid":"fls7tDFJHJwOCWqI1Z0e0Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"- Definición:","guid":"VRfcloS0JaLpzUWAqO0v8A","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"- MM es una neoplasia incurable de células plasmáticas que secretan Ig monoclonal\\N(paraproteína) y/o cadenas ligeras (CL) en exceso, causando daño renal (1).","guid":"DKDdsRovPeg2aflZ6g3Ixw","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"- Representa el 1% de todas las neoplasias y 10% de neoplasias hematológicas (1).","guid":"FafVTKvnKDf1_E5VqCAlfg","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"0","text":"- Fisiopatología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"- Expansión clonal de células plasmáticas secretoras de CL monoclonales nefrotóxicas (1, 2).","guid":"DD8fpT9rgfnUg25BKkcNZw","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"- CL filtradas, endocitadas vía cubilina en túbulo proximal (TP), causando toxicidad directa (2).","guid":"gfd-8mJjlL76X_Oj8_Y4iQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"34","text":"- Exceso de CL lleva a sobrecarga lisosomal, ruptura y liberación de contenido enzimático en TP (1,2).","guid":"LxDpTGS8dUO51CeRwp90pQ","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"34","text":"- Agregación de CL con uromodulina en asa de Henle forma cilindros que obstruyen túbulos distales (1,2).","guid":"E_VYs7NT5p-PffFP_JlJNA","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"34","text":"- Objetivos terapéuticos:","guid":"PycbairSHuFAVSGLldU4Rw","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"- Reducir rápidamente carga tumoral y CL circulantes (3).","guid":"INgZ67WsGF2bp1VdTaAJCg","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"34","text":"- Áreas de investigación:","guid":"JrJB2tMwEJ7svgXqZ83gXA","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"- Inhibidores de endocitosis de CL, inhibidores de agregación CL-uromodulina (2,4).","guid":"4VCUpx7KDjKpGRUfJwJvVQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"0","text":"- Epidemiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"- Incidencia de 40 por millón, el doble en afroamericanos. Edad media al diagnóstico >65 años (1).","guid":"VuyO9fj3xUetxXMT-3n5wg","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"- En Chile, MM representa 1% de cánceres y 14.5% de neoplasias hematológicas (5).","guid":"v8Qxy3BsGyTPIO3miwy1Sg","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"- 50% desarrollará IR en el curso de MM. 20-50% tiene IR al diagnóstico. IRCT en 1-12% (1).","guid":"M_KxJrRLFUcoPkRJWydeBA","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"43","text":"- Causas:","guid":"dYudxBNfuwXy_Y7TEkp1GA","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"- Nefropatía por cilindros:","guid":"tRjD8x2olduZvVs9PZZosg","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"- 30-50% (1).","guid":"qCfxeASIOGiLdbWFRrYAlw","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"- Riñón del MM (nefritis intersticial sin cilindros):","guid":"xjgeAysTGPIoZtvD12iRHw","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"- 20-30% (1).","guid":"qJaXJt5Fc1y0AtA956KfuQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"47","text":"- Amiloidosis AL:","guid":"2j5zUcdc5Aa6lCoG13IpjA","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"- 10%.","guid":"45CxRiwzB83D5dB1Vq3Reg","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"47","text":"- MIDD:","guid":"J8d4ZDeUOypradc1ua1gNA","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"- 5%.","guid":"bcNHRX2Z00Z6x_5GvAHBPg","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"47","text":"- NTA:","guid":"NBkCof4qYyr33MCyobMyCw","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"- 10%.","guid":"RYEnWONVfRszHkRNlUG8mQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"47","text":"- Otras:","guid":"RPyXYJYIIyq3MHggDyUqcg","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"- 5% (1).","guid":"MD4ro3a-qOHNlUrtvIwfvw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"0","text":"- Factores de riesgo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"- GMSI:","guid":"2vZ5K501Ej7y5HgVwuHQGg","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"- RR 25 para MM (6).","guid":"n3J8pDpHNL3dW-iC12agyg","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"- Raza negra:","guid":"ddomxTCvQxw17lA7b12Fmg","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"- RR 2 vs blancos (1).","guid":"ME596apqasgFqUcFZ6wsZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"- Edad >65 años (1).","guid":"CfzibEw7oNUvrLMspySOOA","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"60","text":"- Factores de riesgo renal:","guid":"ZbCY7OKj__MLTqEiSxaNbQ","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"- Hipercalcemia, sepsis, deshidratación, nefrotoxinas (AINEs, contraste) (1,2).","guid":"pnHjaZAK8HEmWtyRdymGLQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"0","text":"- Clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"- MM:","guid":"cd_COfIbhvt-ZG5AKgNsEg","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"- Fatiga, dolor óseo (especialmente dorsal), anemia, hipercalcemia, falla renal (1).","guid":"y4FG5NiBvRpJSJeYCOcfrg","children":[]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"- Cilindros:","guid":"qvaUJf6X5iHZeG--Q0YiRw","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"- IRA con sedimento urinario inactivo . Proteinuria de CL (proteínas de BJ) (1).","guid":"rWk7HeJQ36f5qgddVGSlpw","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"68","text":"- MIDD/Amiloidosis:","guid":"YNHX5qhe3I2nYYgofVkzSw","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"- Proteinuria/sd. nefrótico más frecuente que en cilindros. Hipertensión (1).","guid":"coVhKiapPgNQbnmmGnNDew","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"0","text":"- Factores de mal\\Npronóstico renal:","guid":"0Q4F4L-oF1v-ceYDNSHxOg","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"- Mayor edad, menor TFG basal, mayor excreción de CL (1,7).","guid":"6uBVSec_FBaawAfS_RjMrg","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"- Cilindros en biopsia y fibrosis túbulo-intersticial predicen menor recuperación de función renal (8).","guid":"PZCME9Clg68RIp-mBrClog","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"0","text":"- Estudio:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"- Laboratorio:","guid":"0fm9VMcD_ltvQ_2tZib6AQ","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"- Hemograma, calcemia, creatinina, electroforesis de proteínas (s), inmunofijación (s/o)","guid":"wNVbpE-Qt0Nq6f-c5qwetA","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"- Cuantificación de CL\\Nlibres séricas:","guid":"bJeHq9dWxP130ZoFtl99lg","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"- Relación k/l muy alterada (>100, mediana 7000 mg/L) (1,10).","guid":"Fiw6JUITIeIu-ofoRY9IhA","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"- CLLS >500 mg/L con IRA sugiere fuertemente nefropatía por cilindros","guid":"t0QfoMDmIZUkDWLSkgCMmw","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"- S 98%, E 95%. VPP 0.92 (10).","guid":"u2rCAQ5XvUlHGPSuPvdB2w","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"78","text":"- ¿Biopsia renal?:","guid":"z9IL83H85Gh7tPfQB2Vw8A","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"- No si MM conocido, CLLS >1500 mg/L y sedimento no inflamatorio (1).","guid":"Gd_BPTcIAunVF8dVGaKvyA","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"- Sí en otros casos.","guid":"40Hdj-W30NdPuDAzSE7XTg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"0","text":"- Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"- Criterios diagnósticos\\NMM (IMWG 2014) (11):","guid":"U73eEI4dGr_XHrNYjnSSSw","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"- ≥10% células plasmáticas clonales en MO o\\Nplasmocitoma biopsiado + ≥1 evento definidor de MM.","guid":"boj1KlJvY8YNhsXFkna2lw","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"- Eventos definidores:","guid":"a966Fhvgi7Dfg7-frS-ylA","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"- CRAB (hipercalcemia, falla renal, anemia,\\Nlesiones líticas) o biomarcadores.","guid":"Q77rO55xKLYvHYI8RuoZgg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"88","text":"- Nefropatía por\\Ncilindros (1):","guid":"UwX-P2E1rUBNpe84kkUhRw","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"- Cilindros en biopsia renal o","guid":"9exrNwYkuVJcMawv2UvwDw","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"- Sospecha clínica (IRA, CLLS >1500 mg/L, sedimento no inflamatorio, proteinuria principalmente de BJ)","guid":"I7rV00T-KL_BZODs769v4g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"0","text":"- Diagnósticos\\NDiferenciales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"- Sd. Riñón-MM:","guid":"-5HZsw8U4GNRklRupYND0w","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"- NTA, nefropatías infiltrativas (linfoma, leucemia), amiloidosis, crioglobulinemia.","guid":"VpN-XQMkaVUKsEWT42Apew","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"0","text":"- Tratamiento:","guid":"Ye9kKIhKbBz_OwvT0udxng","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"- Objetivos:","guid":"BxHOPW0ggT0_xIwcu-k3Tg","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"- 1a línea (3).","guid":"yDLAVeaK42zS-mtK6gCY2g","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"- Bortezomib 1.3 mg/m2 SC días 1,4, 8,11.\\NDexametasona 40 mg días 1-4. Ciclos cada 21 días.","guid":"QuWsOgsw1HFlHLjaNMNKuQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"99","text":"- Tripletas (ej. con ciclofosfamida) en jóvenes aptos.\\NLenalidomida si refractario a Bortezomib.","guid":"Oyc0AYjMUU6Rdjq9fwXrOA","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"99","text":"- Recomendaciones\\N(3):","guid":"wLc4EiPtohlIVSO22zzqKw","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"- Reducir rápidamente carga tumoral y CL, revertir IRA, prevenir ERCT (3).","guid":"Yz8G0OpST-LZ2tDBZTj2Tg","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"104","text":"- Suspender nefrotóxicos. Expandir VEC con SF/bicarbonato para diuresis 3 L/día. Evitar diuréticos.","guid":"5trM3UHhq0JLjB1It_oyjw","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"104","text":"- Corregir hipercalcemia (hidratación, bifosfonatos: Zoledronato 4 mg. Denosumab en IR severa).","guid":"42BaD9jBIbC5S0D-XefOiA","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"104","text":"- Iniciar inmediatamente Bortezomib-dexametasona y considerar plasmaféresis o HCO-HD.","guid":"2m7RZo8V9OsKmyW3DlUTnQ","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"104","text":"- TPH en primera remisión si candidato. Profilaxis anti-infecciosa. Eritropoyetina para anemia.","guid":"O77cqkMHNTez9rjX20oHTw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"0","text":"- Seguimiento y\\Npronóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"- Medir CLLS, calcio, creatinina cada ciclo hasta respuesta y cada 2-3 ciclos después (3).","guid":"bmMACu6CNahc1l5VhjRAEQ","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"110","text":"- Respuesta renal:","guid":"VFrCL95AdpGBAPzCPrY4eg","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"- Mejoría TFGe. Al día 21 predice independencia de diálisis (12).","guid":"YykOpkSF0HSWZ1VHBWBTYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"110","text":"- Hematólogo, nefrólogo, enfermera coordinadora, kinesiólogo, psicólogo, asistente social.","guid":"gsaJ8fvqg4ig7_ESpShv2Q","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"110","text":"- Sobrevida promedio\\Nhistórica en diálisis:","guid":"gbI0Cr65iGtOpQbY2qk7Rg","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"- 8 meses (3). En tiempos recientes hasta 7 años (1).","guid":"SBCrci8wPA6ABEwoZ89KEQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"0","text":"- Prevención:","guid":"hcnV99Q0cHB6Dztqf4Kw5g","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"- GMSI:","guid":"4hIxdg8R_z0yFjDQSk2jbQ","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"- Seguimiento con electroforesis de proteínas c/6-12m. Si componente M >1.5 g/dL\\No CLL elevadas, derivar a hematología (13).","guid":"BVnhf68RPIcitQRx-qDUdw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"120","parent":"0","text":"- Tamizaje:","guid":"AMExXFtS45hfSQ407u22Yw","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"- No hay estrategias de tamizaje validadas para MM en población general.","guid":"A4TV5zcfURHlbaNEZRV56A","children":[]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"0","text":"- Aspectos Geriátricos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"- Mayor riesgo de IR y complicaciones del tratamiento. Elegir esquemas según comorbilidades (14).","guid":"b7wywWLtnkJqlgtKg16QXg","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"- Foco en calidad de vida, funcionalidad y prevención del deterioro cognitivo por hipercalcemia (14).","guid":"Q70EhWC4ZLbJqYeJ5vdTYg","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"0","text":"- Referencias:","guid":"jg20yifPB9_WKKEY_nU4HQ","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"- 1. Rajkumar SV. Multiple myeloma: 2020 update on diagnosis, risk-stratification and management. Am J Hematol. 2020;95(5):548–567.","guid":"dM8twIcqnhAvUqy3tu-cRQ","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"- 2. Leung N, et al. Myeloma and the Kidney. In: Comprehensive Clinical Nephrology. 6th ed.; 2019:791-798.","guid":"z-Zf-JN1wS